<p>What if you could get a single platform where you can share your music and videos, reach out to like minded musicians and fans to connect with them? Well, for all established and aspiring musicians looking for one such platform, MusoStar provides all that. MusoStar is a social networking website dedicated solely for musicians. It is a unique concept that brings together the power of both social networking and video sharing at one place.</p>
